name: Men's Proper Dapper Outfit
description: This strangely archaic and rather quaint outfit remains rather attractive and eminently practical. The wearer looks quite dapper with the smart jacket, braced trousers, and jolly bow-tie. Indeed, anyone wearing this outfit might fancy themselves as looking "proper dapper" as they go about their business on the station concourse, or pop into the smart bars of Jita 4-4.
